Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berdirilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dimengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi itu Leviathan saat ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu. Ternyata memang\Nsudah menyusut, ya.
