Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa di desamu ada\Ncalon untuk seleksi kesatria?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagi rakyat jelata seperti kami,\Nitu satu-satunya cara mengubah nasib.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiap tahun, kami mengirim satu calon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menghapus seleksi wilayah,\Njadi silakan kirim beberapa orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ba-Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, bukan apa-apa.\NMaafkan kelancangan saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tersinggung.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi apa yang sedang kau pikirkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan sesuatu\Nyang patut dibesar-besarkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, penyebab calon\Ndari desa kami hanya satu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah karena masalah biaya\Nselama perjalanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harga-harga di ibu kota juga mahal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat gotong royong warga,\Nkami mampu mengirim satu orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena calon terpilih akan memikul\Nharapan seisi desa,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}semua warga pun sangat serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, mari tuntaskan masalah itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin memiliki\Npilihan sebanyak mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sampai masalah itu\Nmenghambat bakat yang ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menanggung semua\Nbiaya perjalanan dan hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya yakin itu akan\Nmembuat warga desa senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun bukankah butuh\Nuang yang sangat banyak?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mempersiapkan\Nsemuanya dari nol.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.13,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dylan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selidiki jumlah rumah kosong\Ndi ibu kota, lalu beli semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus kalau itu sudah mencukupkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau belum, bangunlah asrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesuai titah Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu bahan makanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Segera hubungi pedagang kenalanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga akan pergi ke kota.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan sangat hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikut jumlah perkiraannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat murah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini biaya makan selama seleksi.\NKau tekor besar kalau seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja ini karena permintaan\Ndari Yang Mulia Pangeran Ke-13.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bohong sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pedagang tak mungkin\Nberbisnis pakai perasaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ingin aku melakukan apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya tak menyangka seorang bangsawan\Nbelia mampu memahami sejauh itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Justru bagiku menghamburkan\Nuang itu bagaikan pekerjaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda sangat mengagumkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersamaan dengan seleksi kesatria,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan digelar juga seleksi pelayan istana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya ingin bertanya, adakah kecenderungan\Nkhusus terkait calon yang diterima?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau ingin menempatkan\Nperempuan di dalam istana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rupanya begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kalau ada orang dalam\Nistana yang di bawah kendalinya,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}dia akan mendapatkan\Ninformasi dengan cepat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Andai dia sampai diperintah menemani\Nbaginda saat malam dan menjadi selir,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}keuntungan yang didapat\Nsangatlah banyak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, hal itu\Ntak terkait permintaan Pangeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya sudah menyampaikan tekad\Npada kediaman Pangeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Bayar di muka? Boleh juga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada satu hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dia cocok bagiku,\Naku bisa bantu membujuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama gadis itu\Nmemang cocok bagiku, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya akan memilih gadis\Nyang berkenan bagi Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pangeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.79,0:15:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketajaman wawasan serta\Nkebaikan hati Pangeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya tak berhak menuntut lebih jauh lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika berkenan, izinkan saya mencantumkan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lambang keluarga Pangeran Ke-13\Npada papan usaha saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau berniat tunduk sepenuhnya padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan memaafkan pengkhianat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku mendapatkan plus baru\Nsetelah menjadikan Byron bawahan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}LEVEL: 1/∞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kalau begini terus,\Naku bisa bertambah kuat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}LEVEL: 1/∞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Statusku berkurang?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Air tingkat SS!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa terjadi sesuatu di Almeria?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Zoey, aku akan menghadap Baginda!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arahkan ke istana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampaikan pada kusirnya! Bergegas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ba-Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kejanggalan di Almeria?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengapa kau bisa tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Cara bicaranya ini. Jangan-jangan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda sudah mengetahuinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya menyadari pertandanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Artinya memang terjadi sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau hebat, Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terjadi pemberontakan di Almeria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutmu seberapa besar skalanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kalau diasumsikan berdasarkan\NSS turun menjadi S,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}sekilas statusku berkurang setengah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Namun nyatanya,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}statusku hanya berkurang\Nsatu tingkat saja.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Artinya...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam kondisi saat ini,\Nskalanya masih kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Laporan menyebut jumlahnya 5.000.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Jawaban tepat, ya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekelompok pasukan kecil.\NDi wilayah kekuasaanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak ingin mengatasinya sendiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayangnya, saya merasa itu mustahil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya masih belia dan belum\Nmengenal medan perang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belum tentu para prajurit\Nmau mendengarkan saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:18:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau harus mengutus Pangeran,\Nlebih baik salah satu Kanda saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jawaban tak terduga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak menyangka kau menolakku\Ndengan pertimbangan objektif.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuterima keputusanmu\Ndan memilih orang selainmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau punya saran?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya rasa Kanda Henry cukup cocok.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alasannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berdasarkan skalanya, menindak langsung\Nadalah cara paling tepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai Pangeran yang paling waspada,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kanda Henry pasti akan\Nmengambil langkah pasti.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemilihan yang bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panggil Henry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal ini kesempatanmu.\NApa tak masalah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kekaisaran adalah negeri pejuang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau menorehkan keberhasilan militer,\Nhal baik akan mendatangimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini hal mendadak.\NSaya masih kurang belajar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:19:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meskipun saya bertahan hidup,\Nbisa saja ada prajurit yang mati sia-sia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti biasa, kau logis sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan kereta kudanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Leviathan bereaksi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Yang diincar itu aku.\NAku tak bisa melibatkan Kanda!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengendali Air.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti pemberontak dari Almeria.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cih.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang benar saja.\NOleh anak sekecil itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Walah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah sekuat ini,\Npadahal baru beberapa hari berlalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar pusatnya regu\Npemberontak adalah pasukan berkuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata ada kawanan yang begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alangkah bagusnya kalau\Naku mendapat informasi itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya tak membunuh mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah menundukkan mereka,\Nsaya membiusnya dengan teror Leviathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang seperti mereka\Nbisa memilih bunuh diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga. Mereka masih bernapas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya serahkan mereka pada Kanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, Kanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kanda menyebut pasukan berkuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah produksi kuda\Ndi Almeria cukup lemah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada keperluan apa, Pangeran?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga berdagang di sekitar Almeria, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anggaplah nyawamu bisa hilang\Nkalau informasi ini bocor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terjadi pemberontakan di Almeria.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagian besarnya\Nadalah pasukan berkuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memiliki 10.000 riin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belilah semua pakan kuda sekarang juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesuai perintah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dengan makanan manusianya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau diserahkan pada saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusianya tidak usah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di Almeria tidak ada\Npeternakan kuda perang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berdasarkan Kanda Henry,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kuda-kuda pasukannya\Ndibeli dari daerah luar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti, ada batasan terkait pakan\Nkuda yang bisa dibeli dari warga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau makanan prajurit dikurangi,\Nmaka penjarahan terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pangeran memang menakjubkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:21:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya akan laksanakan sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Seharusnya ini bisa memudahkan\Npertarungan Kandaku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.82,0:22:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an1}Mimpi singkat yang masih tak sampai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kutakut akan peluh\NYang tak kunjung sembuh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Siluet terpantul di tepi jendela{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kenanganku bersamamu\Nperlahan memudar{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.80,0:22:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Diterangi sinar rembulan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kulihat dirimu bersinar\NBagai bintang nun jauh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:22:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Walau musim berganti, waktu berlalu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Rasaku padamu tidak{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Harapku agar sajak cinta abadi ini\NKian sampai padamu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.58,0:23:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Walau kutahu kan terwujud\NAku tetap memimpikannya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Air mataku mengering{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an3}Pemandangan mengabur\NDi seberang keabadian{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an3}Walau aku terlepas bayang-bayangmu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.13,0:23:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Hatiku kan terpaut di sisimu{\i0}
